I'm burning this off for my gf and I watched it to make sure it didn't need subs, and all that goodness, and I noticed something.

Either this is not the final cut, or parts of the movie have been changed since the release of the trailer.

Ex. At no point does Darren yell "This is boring!" to Steven like in the trailer. He also doesn't climb the inside of the tent in front of the snake-boy.

Not sure why these parts aren't in this cut, but like I said, it's either not the final cut or those parts have been removed.
